- Backend test runner used `npx vitest` from repo root, which is non-deterministic in CI/workspaces and can fail to resolve `vitest` from backend-local deps when root context lacks it.
- Angular typed forms error (`TS7053`) came from indexing `responseForm.controls` with a dynamic string while the form was inferred as `{}` (no string index signature).

